By: Huang Po
---
As soon as the mouth is opened, evils spring forth. People either neglect the
root and speak of the branches, or neglect the reality of the ‘illusory’
world and speak only of Enlightenment. Or else they chatter of cosmic
activities leading to transformations, while neglecting the Substance from
which they spring.
